    Library Class:
        Description: Represents a library that manages books, members, and loans.
        Attributes:
            books: List of Book objects available in the library.
            members: List of Member objects registered with the library.
            loans: List of Loan objects representing current loans in the library.
        Methods:
            addBook(book: Book): Adds a new book to the library.
            registerMember(member: Member): Registers a new member with the library.
            findBook(isbn: String): Book: Finds a book in the library by its ISBN.
            findMember(memberId: String): Member: Finds a member in the library by their member ID.
            issueLoan(book: Book, member: Member): Issues a loan for a book to a member.
            returnLoan(book: Book, member: Member): Records the return of a borrowed book.

    Admin Class:
        Description: Represents an administrator who has special privileges to manage the library.
        Attributes:
            username: Username of the admin.
            password: Password of the admin.
        Methods:
            issueLoan(library: Library, book: Book, member: Member): Issues a loan for a book to a member.
            returnLoan(library: Library, book: Book, member: Member): Records the return of a borrowed book.
            addBook(library: Library, book: Book): Adds a new book to the library.
            registerMember(library: Library, member: Member): Registers a new member with the library.

    Book Class:
        Description: Represents a book available in the library.
        Attributes:
            title: Title of the book.
            author: Author of the book.
            isbn: ISBN (International Standard Book Number) of the book.
            copies: Number of copies available in the library.
        Methods:
            displayDetails(): Displays the details of the book.
            isAvailable(): boolean: Checks if the book is available for borrowing.

    Member Class:
        Description: Represents a member of the library who can borrow books.
        Attributes:
            name: Name of the member.
            memberId: Unique ID of the member.
            borrowedBooks: List of Book objects borrowed by the member.
        Methods:
            borrowBook(book: Book): Allows the member to borrow a book.
            returnBook(book: Book): Allows the member to return a borrowed book.

    Loan Class:
        Description: Represents a loan record for a book borrowed by a member.
        Attributes:
            book: Book object being borrowed.
            member: Member object who borrowed the book.
            issueDate: Date when the book was issued.
            returnDate: Date when the book was returned (null if not returned yet).
        Methods:
            issue(): Records the issuance of the book.
            returnBook(): Records the return of the book.